Soaring over the landscape, she approached the supposed Decepticon named 
Carnation. 

Coming within ranger, she soon transformed in mid-flight then landed a little 
distant from Carnation. she didn't remember this one. Of course, since 
Galvatron's rule, she had been rather.. disconnected.. from the Decepticons.
